 \"@iden3/bigarray\";\n\nA = new BigArray(1000000);\n\nfor (let i=0; i<1000000; i++) {\n\tA.push({\n\t\tnum: i;\n\t\tsquare: i*i;\n\t});\n}\n\nconsole.log(A[3].num * A[700000].square);\n```\n","readmeFilename":"README.md"}